fix: pin get_service() to version="v20" to prevent v23 mismatch

google-ads SDK 29.x defaults to v23 for get_service(), but all code
builds v20 protobuf objects. Passing a v20 request to a v23 service
client triggers "Invalid constructor input for MutateXxxRequest"
because the v23 client tries to re-wrap the proto in its own types.

Fixed 82 get_service() calls across 77 files to explicitly pass
version="v20".
